  <div>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_forensic_learning_disability_service">Forensic Learning Disability Service</xref>
 is a type of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_mental_health_service">Mental Health Service</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_forensic_learning_disability_service">Forensic Learning Disability Service</xref>
 provides specialist forensic assessment and treatment of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_forensic_mental_health_patient">Forensic Mental Health Patients</xref>
 who also have a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_learning_disability">Learning Disability</xref>.        </p>
